{
  "texts": [
    "Wazuh provides two RBAC modes; allow list mode where everything is forbidden and the administrator needs to configure the roles to allow permissions, and a block list mode where everything is allowed and the administrator needs to restrict permissions for roles.",
    "OSSIM provides three RBAC roles, Read-Only, Analyst and Manager.",
    "Elastic Security allows assigning roles to users or groups and assigning privileges to various roles.",
    "Monster also provides fine-grained role-based access control to indices, documents and fields.",
    "Next, we evaluated another important feature of a SIEM system which is fault tolerance."
  ]
}